race.description: Aussie Night Markets Super Mdn Plate
race.comment: Bjorn Baker's Extreme Choice first starter EXTRAGLOW (6) has been most impressive in his last couple of trials, winning both by wide spaces. Has to measure up on race day but he is in good hands and looks well above average. MAGIC FLAMES (8) settled handy then worked home well but found one better when resuming over this distance at Wyong last start. Should race up on the speed again and with that run under the belt will be tough to hold out. New Michael Freedman acquisition PAZYRYK (10) lines up for the first time since failing on debut at Canterbury 11 months ago. In the market on that occasion so probably has more to offer. HAMMURABI (1) debuts. Has trialled no less than six times, with the latest effort the pick of them. Watch the betting. DENISE'S GAL (5) probably gets a soft lead and might give them something to catch.
